author: Hannah Ryan
title: "I've Never Seen Anything Like This": Asylum Seekers Are Overwhelming This Charity Because Of The Coronavirus
description: Many refugees and asylum seekers are losing their jobs, but aren’t eligible for welfare. How are they meant to live? View Entire Post ›
content:
Carolina Gottardo said her job is changing rapidly at first by the week, then by the day.
It has been incredible, Gottardo, the director of the Jesuit Refugee Service (JRS) charity in Sydney, Australia, told BuzzFeed News. Ive never seen anything like this.… [+5355 chars]
